{"title":"致“老马”","authors":["郑伯农"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":11,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致“老马”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑伯农"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你写过老马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你正是识途的老马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏着身后的荆棘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披负着前路的花香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰骋了一辈子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕耘了一辈子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下了坚韧不拔的足迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下了万众争诵的华章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那回肠荡气的呼唤与沉吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！老马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花已铺满脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦旗已挂满四壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可否准备卸去征鞍？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲停脚步，卸担息肩？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代在召唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前路还漫长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老马正奋足扬鬃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带领着不甘伏枥的马群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向二十一世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向诗的崇高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写于臧克家老人九十华诞"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}